{"word":"G1961 - ἐπιμένω - epiménō - ep-ee-men'-o - Abide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιμένω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epiménō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-men'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Abide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிலைத்திரு, தங்கு, தரித்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to stay at or with; to tarry still; still to abide, to continue, remain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G3306 - μένω - ménō - men'-o/3306\">G3306</a>; to <i>stay over</i>, that is, <i>remain</i> (figuratively <i>persevere</i>): - abide (in), continue (in), tarry.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}